00:22:14.850 --> 00:22:18.780
about these issues, and,
also, invite questions

00:22:18.780 --> 00:22:21.632
from the audience, which
somewhere there are

00:22:21.632 --> 00:22:22.840
pieces of paper going around.

00:22:22.840 --> 00:22:26.520
Cards, and you can submit those
to people gathering those,

00:22:26.520 --> 00:22:28.980
and we will try to
integrate as many of those

00:22:28.980 --> 00:22:33.300
